mxTextCell.label: Encrypt and decrypt key words by using the resources color coding.

mxTextCell.title: Text
mxTextCell.label:
- Key words can be encrypted by using color combinations;
 - Decrypting the color combinations can be done by using pools that exclude possibilities
   or by using registers which count the correct elements in order to detect the key word.
